              "heading_text": "What is \"Mounting\"",
              "anchor_id": "what-is-mounting",
              "section_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/static-files/#what-is-mounting",
              "section_text_parts": [
                "\"Mounting\" means adding a complete \"independent\" application in a specific path, that then takes care of handling all the sub-paths.",
